#Benjamin Masi  
###Ruby on Rails web developer at Metis run by Thoughtbot  
  
###Projects:    
[Roomr](https://github.com/benmmasi/roomr) - Check out the SQL queries I wrote in the Message model, and the   next_for method in the Question model.    
[Taskr](https://github.com/benmmasi/taskr) - Check out the app/assets/javascripts directory to see the work I did    
in javascript, jQuery, and AJAX.  
[Craigstr](https://github.com/mcquackers/craigstr) - Check out the spec directory to see the tests I wrote using  
Rspec and Capybara.
